{"tid":1782092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"**九份茶舍免費急救先修班**","createTime":"2019-12-13T16:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T12:21:27.000Z","uid":171338,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8dbc157f09ef460f78b29f301139b976f84d0db8","tid":1782092,"uid":171338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"From九份茶舍FB Page<br />\n<br />\n**九份茶舍免費急救先修班**<br />\n幾經辛苦，我哋呢個First Aid班終於搞得成啦！<br />\n因為時間倉猝，￼呢個班暫時未能提供考試同證書，只會教授基本嘅急救知識。￼雖然係咁，我哋絕對唔會Hea做，￼導師係由一班「資深院前醫護人員」教授，如果今次反應理想，我哋會盡快安排一啲正式嘅急救考試班比大家。￼￼首先再講多次，今次只會接受學生申請，同埋一經接納懇請大家唔好放飛機，善用資源。￼(先到先得，額滿即止)<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n日期：18 Dec (Wed) 1800-2200 /<br />\n22 Dec (Sun) 0900-1300 / 1400 -1800<br />\n(共三班，每班25人)<br />\n地點：【Party Moment】旺角亞皆老街56-62號利安大廈1樓62室(旺角地鐵站D3出口步行2分鐘)<br />\n年齡：13歲以上學生<br />\n報名表格：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/5sifwjaEeJ9M9YSm6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F5sifwjaEeJ9M9YSm6&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=352fb32e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/5sifwjaEeJ9M9YSm6</a><br />\n<br />\n參加者上課日期將會隨機抽籤￼，取錄名單將會個別另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n會教授以下內容：<br />\n* Hand only cpr +/- aed<br />\n* 止血<br />\n* 呼吸急症<br />\n* 骨骼關節損傷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2074082079568590/posts/2368126060164189?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2074082079568590%2Fposts%2F2368126060164189%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIHr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=41edcde4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2074082079568590/posts/2368126060164189?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"dfb9f207fcd7de48c663b3254d0aba8cb0e15f86","tid":1782092,"uid":171338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T16:07:14.000Z","msg":"Pushhhhh"},{"pid